@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pxypta(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.20 / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.77) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.10)))
    v0 = ((v2 + wp.cos(tmp + 0.90)) - 0.87)
    tmp = (0.36 - wp.sin((v2 + 0.36 / tmp + 0.53)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.93) / wp.cos((v0 + 0.81 * v1 + 0.43)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.56)) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.93 / v0 + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
